    "201709": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Kamisato Ayaka",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "#Well, {NICKNAME}? How did it go?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm not sure..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We lit the firework and ran away..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Well done. Let's wait for news from Sayu."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "After some time..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sayu",
                    "T": "*panting*..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sayu",
                    "T": "I know exercise helps you grow, but this was a little too much exercise..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sayu",
                    "T": "I feel so dizzy... Everyone is spinning..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sayu",
                    "T": "No, I can't sleep yet. There was something important I was supposed to do first... Oh, right, yeah. I got it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sayu",
                    "T": "I didn't know how to find the document you guys were talking about, so I just swiped a whole bunch of stuff that looked suspicious."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sayu",
                    "T": "Here you go... I'm going to sleep now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Thoma",
                    "T": "Milady, what are we looking at?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "This sealed envelope must be an official report that the Tenryou Commission is preparing to present to the Shogun."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "In addition, we have... correspondence with the Fatui."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "It seems that Guuji Yae was right. They have been fomenting unrest behind the scenes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, this should be ample evidence. Please take them to <color=#00E1FFFF>Guuji Yae</color>. I trust she will have a plan for the next step."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "I will also gather some people to try and root out the rest of the Fatui in Inazuma."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Thoma",
                    "T": "Still, mind yourself when you face the Shogun. I still get goosebumps just thinking about her drawing that blade..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Again, we'll just have to trust Guuji Yae. She is close to the Shogun, so maybe she will have a way..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "If Paimon remembers correctly, it should be time for our meeting with Yae Miko soon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's pack up our things and get ready to head to the <color=#00E1FFFF>Grand Narukami Shrine</color>."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
