    "201901": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Signora",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "The way people charge in here as they please... So uncivilized."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "If I didn't know this was Tenshukaku, I might have mistaken it for some kind of street market."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Have you learned your lesson now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh no, what has she done to Kujou Sara..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "The right to punish Inazumans for their crimes is mine alone. Not yours, Signora."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "...Then I apologize, Almighty Shogun."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Signora!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "I know, I know, you can't get me out of your mind. But you really don't need to call my name all the time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Don't go thinking I'm surprised to see you here. I'm well aware that you hate me, with the way you follow me around like a dark shadow."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're secretly distributing Delusions..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're trying to seize control of Inazuma..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Ah, so you came to expose my crimes in front of the Shogun?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Hehehe... I'm just a Snezhnayan diplomat. I'm afraid I have no idea what you're talking about."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "She doesn't take us seriously at all..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "For all who have lost their Visions..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "For all who have been harmed by Delusions..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Stop talking about people and things that I care nothing about."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "They were nobodies to begin with, and their names will be forgotten. But now, at least, they get to be building blocks in the grand revolution to realize eternity..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Is that not the greatest honor they could hope for in their tiny little lives?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Almighty Shogun... do correct me if I'm wrong?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "For Venti's Gnosis..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And for the people of Liyue you imperiled..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "That's ancient history. You certainly love to hold a grudge."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "The Tsaritsa's dream is the noblest and purest thing in all the world."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "These other mundane details you insist on mentioning... They're just necessary sacrifices. That's all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's time for me to put a stop to this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "You? Stop me? Hahaha..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "For what it's worth, I've grown tired of seeing you around as well. But I didn't have you down as someone quite so foolhardy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Before you go saying something you can't take back, remember that you're Inazuma's most wanted criminal... I suggest you consider your circumstances very carefully."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Charging into Tenshukaku uninvited and lecturing me in front of the Shogun wasn't the brightest move. Don't you think it's time you stopped digging?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "I'm not sure you realize quite how much distance there is between us, both in status... and in strength."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I challenge you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...To a duel before the throne!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Proceed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "My, you're full of surprises today... So you've learned to make the law of the land work for you too, hmm?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "I'll admit that I never expected to be in a situation where the two of us were on equal footing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "You are aware... that the loser must die? Are you sure this is what you want?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Signora",
                    "T": "Hehehe... then I will deign to share this last dance with you... till death do us part."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
