    "202003": {
        "Desc": "Talk to the Raiden Shogun within the Plane of Euthymia",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Indulge my curiosity. What is the reason that I find you standing here before me once again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Do you hope your foolhardiness will shelter those people? Or... was it simply a means of seeking an audience with me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Fatui have deceived the Raiden Shogun."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Vision Hunt Decree should never have existed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Oh? Surely you didn't rouse me from my state of eternal meditation only to tell me this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "If so, then you underestimate me. I am quite well-informed about the Vision Hunt Decree."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You know everything that's going on outside?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Not so. Only everything that pertains to eternity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "The Vision Hunt Decree has my tacit approval."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "The Fatui's actions thus far do not constitute a threat to eternity, otherwise... they would have been purged long ago."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But the Vision Hunt Decree is damaging."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It comes at a great cost to the people of Inazuma."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Individual ambition is inherently incompatible with eternity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "What you might not realize is that all too often... people have far more to lose by chasing their dreams."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Consider this — no one will lose their life on account of having their Vision taken away..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Rather, those who have lost their lives are the ones who insisted on pursuing their own aspirations, are they not?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Teppei..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Traveler, your existence is unique in my eyes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "There seems to be limitless uncertainty in you. To put it another way, you are the furthest thing from eternity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "So I won't insist that you comprehend the meaning of my actions. What matters is that I tread the path of eternity on my people's behalf."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This is your Plane of Euthymia..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It is created by your consciousness, yes?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "That's right. I'm surprised you understand it so well..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Anyway. You're looking for a chance to shake my will... aren't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm not here to debate your ideas."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm here to demolish them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "So be it. Well then, you who would defy eternity... Time for you to enlighten me."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
