    "202005": {
        "Desc": "Talk to the Raiden Shogun",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "You've lost, Ei."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "...Yes, I have."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Why can you not trust your people, and in the power of their ambitions?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "These ambitions have transcended space and time. They are something that no one can snuff out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "When people move forward with all their might..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "They can surpass the gods' expectations."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And even take over the work of the gods."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Is this the lesson you learned from your journey in Liyue?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "There are nations where humans cast their god aside and stride forward...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "So, are we to just abandon the notion of progress... for the sake of wishful thinking?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "...You and I have both witnessed the great loss that progress can bring."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Eternity... eternity is the only way..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "The Heavenly Principles... Irrelevant nonsense as far as I am concerned."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "When all's said and done, all you really want is to protect your beloved Inazuma, forever and ever. Isn't that right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "That would be something of an oversimplification."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "But is this nation worth existing for eternity?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Stripped of ambitions, stripped of the potential for change, it does nothing more than simply... exist. It is a hollow shell of a nation."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Huh. I wonder what loss would it really be to anyone if such a nation were destroyed?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Miko, retract your words."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Never-changing eternity is the promise I made to my people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "But what your people need from you is not your promises. They want your attention... your divine gaze."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "...You mean Visions?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Humans have a lifespan of barely a hundred years. They cannot afford to bear any extra losses."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "But I have experienced it all. That is why I have chosen to guide them along the correct path toward eternity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "*sigh*..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "But eternity is far too cruel a fate for you, Ei."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "For me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Not only have you stopped paying attention to the world, but you have stopped paying attention to yourself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "It must have been terribly lonely here, all alone, for centuries on end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "But it is necessary..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "You will miss much by refusing progress... You seek to prevent loss, but have you considered all you are losing by remaining here in stasis for all eternity?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "You are obviously lonely, and yet for the sake of eternity you choose to stretch your loneliness out to infinity..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Tell me this. Why is the sky here that was once so dark glowing again? Why now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "This is your Plane of Euthymia. It's your inner world."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "So it can only mean... that you are happy to see me again. You have found the loneliness here unbearable for a long time now, haven't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "I... have nothing to say to that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Hehehe, oh, but I have so much to say to you. Let me tell you all that has happened over the last few centuries."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "How long will that take?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "As a fox envoy, I have an excellent memory. I recall every detail of the last few centuries with perfect clarity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "So it will probably take me another few centuries to relay it to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Heh... hehe... Miko, I never thought I would have the chance to meet with you like this again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "*sigh* Seeing you again is a change to eternity... and a very nice surprise."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Hehe, since you are willing to admit that, I suppose that means we can still be friends?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "What a childish conversation this is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "Anyway. Now that I have been defeated by you and your plan, I will honor your wish to abolish the Vision Hunt Decree."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raiden Shogun",
                    "T": "But with regards to eternity and the question of whether this nation should move forward, I need time to give it some thought."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Hehe, you are the one who's been acting like a child from the very beginning."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
